snippet.textDisplay:
Whenever I felt like crying, they made me feel like dancing ! Phir Socha, kis shaoor ke aansoo hain ye andar.. and I realized Khushi ya gham ke aansoo nhi hain per se. These are an awe state's tears ! Like..  can't explain fairly.. it's like when I witness something THIS Beautiful.. visually joyful and captivating, musically breathtaking and exciting and vocally outstanding toh main emotional Kaise na banun!? Especially in times where music and art are not taken so seriously.. ALL MY LOVE AND RESPECT for the whole team 🖤It's beyond all words and names now. Maghron La and Aayi ay are my top favourites till now. It's just pure emotions. Also.. Yar the cuuuteness and naughtiness are next level.. could never expect or imagine that. Like, Ali Zafar's rockstar was the top chulbuli bulbuli vibe for me 🙊😆.. Rozeo is so cute ! Sabri sisters ki Kya baat ! Why so khoobsurat why ! Dil lootne wala mauhaul hai for real ! Shall I be talking more about the music or the designs or the frames .. mujhe toh nhi pata 🤷🏻‍♀️ The entry .. the radio sounds.. the first beat which catches you till the end and even Uske baad🖤 Hairstyles and phools everywhere uff ! Kya tha yeh ✨ EVERY  frame is a work of art and I mean it .. EVERY frame ! Not a single disappointing one. Rozeo's entry is mind-blowing and funnnn at all levels and that "I like it" is a hook. Lyrics 🔥🎯 The not so usual mehendi style ! The daaancerss omg ! They nailed it. Honestly I was missing masterpieces because of my confused and dukhi state of mind and I'm so thankful to everyone who kept encouraging me (nagging too) to see this 🤭🙈 I'm so honoured to have a small, outstanding and artistic community on my YouTube. And I'm sooo thrilled to be witnessing this in my lifetime.
Dil le le bas.. 🎯❤️ Everyone involved in this season and this legacy has my WHOLE HEART.
Hana.
